==English==
===Adjective===
'''[[nothing]] [[special]]'''
#{{idiom}} ordinary, run-of-the-mill
#: ''The sandwich was plain old junk food, '''nothing special'''.''

===Noun===
#{{idiom}} nothing worth discussing; nothing that the speaker wants to mention

Often used as an evasion or conversation-stopper, when nosy queries are made. It's an indirect way of telling someone to "[[mind his own business]]".